::Battera/Feline::

Battera::

She looked at the others standing in the room.  She smiled and looked 
around."Well, if no one objects, I'll go and let my friend in.  I 
will have him stop by the bridge for a security check, if that's 
alright with everyone." She curtsied and walked out.  She went down 
the hall and went to the entrance.  She opened the hatch and looked 
out.  There was CyberShark, standing there.  She smiled, "Hello 
there." She chuckled, "Long time no see."  She had a sweet smile and 
loving look in her eyes. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Feline:

She got that parts ready in the CR room.  She had spare boards and 
wires ready.  She had arms and legs, chest and other body parts and 
plating.  Joints and sauldering supplies out and ready.  She had it 
all set out on the counter tops and in containers.  Tools were set 
out and put out, ready for use.  The place looked like a surgery room 
with everything ready for a procedure, except a patient.  Dinobot and 
Travatron had not yet been rescued yet.  She smiled at her work.

"Oh, fixing them up will be no problem at all, no matter what the 
damage."  She smiled gleefully at her handy work and walked out of 
the CR room.  She headed for the mess hall, humming and whistling.
She swayed her hips and twitched her tail as she walked.  She kept 
her eyes straight, incase she passed any other bots.
